{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-project-js","path":"/portfolio/bezos-api/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"35c944df-62c6-5e51-8d65-b1183d0fd973","html":"<p><a href=\"https://github.com/bezos-api/bezos-api/actions/workflows/ci.yml\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://github.com/bezos-api/bezos-api/actions/workflows/ci.yml/badge.svg?branch=main\" alt=\"Continuous Integration\"></a> <a href=\"https://github.com/bezos-api/bezos-api/actions/workflows/deploy-lambda.yml\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://github.com/bezos-api/bezos-api/actions/workflows/deploy-lambda.yml/badge.svg?branch=main\" alt=\"Deploy Lambda\"></a></p>\n<p>API to fetch a random Jeff Bezos quote deployed to AWS.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>To see tickets - view the status of the <a href=\"https://github.com/orgs/bezos-api/projects/1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">GitHub Project</a>.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>This is a serverless API using Amazon Gateway API connected to AWS Lambda. Deployments are automated using AWS CDK (w/ GitHub Actions) to provision resources and permissions automatically.</p>\n<h2>ðŸ”¥ API Endpoint</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"sh\"><pre class=\"language-sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">$ <span class=\"token function\">curl</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-L</span> https://czrnt8u0m7.execute-api.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/prod/api/random</code></pre></div>\n<h3>Example <code class=\"language-text\">JSON</code> response</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"content\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Good intentions don't work, mechanisms do\"</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>Contact</h2>\n<p>Spencer Lepine - <a href=\"https://twitter.com/spencerlepine\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">@spencerlepine</a></p>\n<p>Project link: <a href=\"https://github.com/bezos-api/bezos-api\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://github.com/bezos-api/bezos-api</a></p>\n<hr>\n<p>Also find me here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://twitter.com/SpencerLepine\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Twitter (@spencerlepine)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/spencerlepine\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">GitHub (@spencerlepine)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/in/spencer-lepine/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">LinkedIn</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"Bezos API","tech":["AWS Lambda","GitHub Actions","Amazon Gateway API","AWS CDK"],"github":"https://github.com/bezos-api/bezos-api","external":null,"description":"Random Jeff Bezos quote API w/ automated deployment/provisioning with GitHub Actions to AWS CDK (serverless).","slug":"/portfolio/bezos-api","thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1.530612244897959,"src":"/static/e8805c930952a1bad720ac22d170a238/8c332/bezos-thumbnail.png","srcSet":"/static/e8805c930952a1bad720ac22d170a238/95f17/bezos-thumbnail.png 150w,\n/static/e8805c930952a1bad720ac22d170a238/37d5a/bezos-thumbnail.png 300w,\n/static/e8805c930952a1bad720ac22d170a238/8c332/bezos-thumbnail.png 600w,\n/static/e8805c930952a1bad720ac22d170a238/03620/bezos-thumbnail.png 900w,\n/static/e8805c930952a1bad720ac22d170a238/ea2b4/bezos-thumbnail.png 1076w","sizes":"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px"}}}},"fileAbsolutePath":"/Users/notspencer/workplace/portfolio-site-v2/content/portfolio/bezos-api/bezos-api.md"}}]}},"pageContext":{}},"staticQueryHashes":["1994492073"]}